    public abstract class DSpaceRestRepository<T extends RestAddressableModel,​ID extends Serializable>
extends AbstractDSpaceRestRepository
implements org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<T,​ID>, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanNameAware
    Base class for any Rest Repository. Adds a DSpaceContext to the normal Spring Data Repository methods signature.
